// Signing.xcconfig — Personal code-signing config for VBTrainer.
//
// Fill in your Apple Developer Team ID once and never touch this file again.
// Find it at https://developer.apple.com/account → Membership → Team ID.
// Free / personal Apple ID also has a Team ID (10-char alphanumeric).
//
// After editing the line below, run:
//
//   git update-index --skip-worktree Signing.xcconfig
//
// to keep your Team ID out of commits. Or run scripts/setup-signing.sh which
// does the skip-worktree for you.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
